<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 10. Linear discriminant analysis of characters from leaves, staminate inflorescences and staminate flowers of the five a priori groups of the Curarea toxicofera complex: A plot of scores of function 1 and function 2 B histograms of the first discriminant function values showing the positions of the five a priori defined groups, al. = allpahuayo, iq = Curarea iquitana, tm = Curarea tomentocarpa, to = Curarea toxicofera and uc = ucayali, respectively." , "Figure 21. Geographic distribution of Curarea iquitana and C. tecunarum, for the latter selected specimens only, because most of the specimens are sterile." , "Figure 20. Curarea iquitana (photograph of the type of Chondrodendron iquitanum, Tessmann 4196, B)." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/211307" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/211318" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/211317" .

